Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  刹那他无论如何也要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果去拉格朗日5  在那里避难的琳达她们也在继续研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利的话恐怕还能拿到之前提案的新装备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到那之后还能给Gundam进行补给和修理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我给舰船掌舵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉赛负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有人来保护托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让我上战场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾和斯米尔诺夫上校约定过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,索玛·佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续这种战斗的话  总有一天你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密会迂回吸引敌人注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这期间就拜托你们趁机与发信人联络
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是救人吧？  救人的话我就帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的事抱歉了  太过感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没资格当Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  干掉那些改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是作为卡塔隆  也不是作为Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为我自己的意志而与他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密  第一  第三舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弹射时机交由OO控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO  刹那·F·清英  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Raiser  沙慈·克洛斯罗德  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Raiser  对接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO-Raiser  飞往拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光学摄像机捕捉到Celestial Being的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在改变航向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续追击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打败了Celestial Being的话  反对势力的士气也会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些散漫的特殊许可持有者一点也靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不辜负片桐司令的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就以压倒性的战力击败那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊？  连亚琉都被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明是改革者的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不客气了！ OO！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种作战方式  不仅仅是MS的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO的驾驶员已经开始革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？ 在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话就说不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说他是纯种？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那·F·清英…他会成为人类中的第一个改革者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里啊  准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新型MA的补给…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准尉  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说了别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你们了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我和准尉的特别命令已经下达了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我一同前往  我这就去找古德曼中将申请许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不认为你能跟上我和准尉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离到达目标地点还有几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的你有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  就由你来改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代替没能将这些改变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要改变  不管前面会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,席琳么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擦伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没事真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要上宇宙去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和联邦的政变派幸存者接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,支部大部分都被摧毁  继续留在地面上很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是在宇宙的卡塔隆的战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  还有人正以与我们和Celestial Being不同的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,传达自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  玛丽娜公主的歌正在传唱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜的歌传向了世界…  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为人们都在追求和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通过玛丽娜公主的歌  消除纷争  一同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只知道否定别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定都看不到人们相互理解的这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相互理解的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜一直在追求这个  相信着这条路的前景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,指定地点没有人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  Celestial Being真的会来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不这样的话  世界就会变成改革者的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变成李本兹·阿尔马克的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜·崔尼蒂是什么时候倒向改革者那边的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别光是问我  自己也想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你这样  我才不得已成为王家的继承人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为哥哥你没有成为继承人的器量  我的人生被扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才期望着世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有地位  名誉  资产作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我要让人生重来  我要得到只属于自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你陪我到最后  红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个乱七糟八的理由算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留美！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留美！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,留…留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就由…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只会逞能而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要追吗  要追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样计划就能加速进行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不属于伊奥利亚也不属于李本兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是属于我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS无法到达指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机体的控制就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里面吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,王留美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？  受伤了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里标记了吠陀本体的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀本体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果改革者知道了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀就会被转移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽快把吠陀夺过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就别担心我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟你们走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为志不同道不合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四年不见了  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  要是不想失去Gundam的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就请回应我的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心愿是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真真正正的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我格拉哈姆·艾卡  期盼与你一决高下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是受李本兹指使的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不惜这么做就那么想一决胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玷污了我的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺去了同胞和恩师的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,粉碎了身为Flag机师自豪感的不是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是你和Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这已跨越了爱  超越了恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成了我的宿命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宿命？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想嘲笑我的一厢情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但别忘了最初实行武力介入的就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这男人又是一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们所扭曲的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈  控制交给这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我期望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Masurao·改·Susanoo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驱逐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是Celestial Being还是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都将像哥哥那样献上生命完成变革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我将在那美妙的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不会有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过吗  我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你唯命是从只是为了活命而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍听话些马上就博取了信任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你的使命结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你对人任意摆布的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能活命我什么都会干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我能幸福就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  听从改革者摆布也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥们的仇还没有报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时机一到就狠狠地咬断他们的咽喉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的使命也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须给肆意妄为的人以惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的审判者也将要出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说审判者？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…那家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣  可以为哥哥们报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  某种意义上说这也是报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了妈妈和爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机体是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了路易丝家人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  路易丝·哈莱维
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冤冤相报…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说要全力战斗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家人的仇？我也有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为不幸的只有自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被创造出的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被指使着战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能…死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  妈妈和爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连这话都没来得及说出口！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畜牲！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Throne被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能专注到战斗中来吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr.武士道和Gundam激战中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准尉的机体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我报了仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打败Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  爸爸  你们在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…夸奖我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说声「做得好」吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是为了此刻而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕成为改革者的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有这武士道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不惜做到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精力战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于觉醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经进入涅磐了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是粒子汇集之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格制造出Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  制造出GN Drive的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,武力介入只是布局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奥利亚的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引导人类走向革新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我…要进行变革
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺回吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了强行突破A-LAWS舰队的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「为了未来」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是那场战争关系到未来的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算背负罪行也要力争到底
